Here I go!

85
00:03:48,938 --> 00:03:50,368
You go down like this.

86
00:03:50,638 --> 00:03:51,738
Let's move over there.

87
00:03:52,838 --> 00:03:54,237
- Should we? - There. It will be dangerous here.

88
00:03:54,238 --> 00:03:55,578
(Jung Ah and Si Eon move over to a good spot to watch.)

89
00:03:55,748 --> 00:03:58,118
