93
00:04:06,488 --> 00:04:08,287
This is a great spot to watch.

94
00:04:08,288 --> 00:04:09,288
(Getting ready at a great spot that makes you want popcorn)

95
00:04:09,289 --> 00:04:10,527
Hold onto it like this.

96
00:04:10,528 --> 00:04:11,957
