I will hold onto it.

104
00:04:27,408 --> 00:04:28,677
Are you ready? Tell me when you're ready.

105
00:04:28,678 --> 00:04:29,748
Hold on!

106
00:04:30,148 --> 00:04:31,148
(Groaning)

107
00:04:31,748 --> 00:04:33,977
- Run before the jump? - Right.

108
00:04:33,978 --> 00:04:35,587
I'm holding onto it. Hold on.

109
