110
00:04:37,118 --> 00:04:38,318
Run.

111
00:04:38,588 --> 00:04:39,918
- Let's go! - I'm so scared!

112
00:04:40,018 --> 00:04:41,587
One!

113
00:04:41,588 --> 00:04:42,887
- Two! - Two!

114
00:04:42,888 --> 00:04:44,028
- Three! - Three!

115
00:04:46,658 --> 00:04:47,828
Three!

116
00:04:51,228 --> 00:04:52,238
- Three! - Three!

117
00:04:56,038 --> 00:04:57,038
(Laughing)

118
00:04:58,778 --> 00:05:01,378
(After making a brave jump,)

119
00:05:02,278 --> 00:05:04,377
(her hands slip off.)

120
00:05:04,378 --> 00:05:07,577
(Diving in while holding her breath)

121
00:05:07,578 --> 00:05:09,818
Oh, no!

122
00:05:10,518 --> 00:05:12,317
(I can't do this.)

123
00:05:12,318 --> 00:05:14,558
(Laughing)

124
00:05:15,088 --> 00:05:17,358
(Laughing)

125
00:05:17,858 --> 00:05:20,598
(All she can do is laugh.)

126
00:05:20,987 --> 00:05:22,827
She doesn't have the strength to hold on.

127
00:05:23,428 --> 00:05:26,098
- One more time. - One more time. This is tough.

128
00:05:26,998 --> 00:05:28,607
- You'll try one more time? - Yes.

129
