132
00:05:35,508 --> 00:05:38,048
Let's go, Jun Myun!

133
00:05:38,178 --> 00:05:39,878
- Let's go! - Let's go!

134
00:05:41,018 --> 00:05:43,217
(I, Park Jun Myun,)

135
00:05:43,218 --> 00:05:44,218
Look at the face she's making.
(will not fail.)

136
