139
00:05:51,928 --> 00:05:53,158
One!

140
00:05:53,498 --> 00:05:55,268
- Two! - Two!

141
00:05:55,428 --> 00:05:57,597
(Show us, Jun Myun.)

142
00:05:57,717 --> 00:05:59,417
- Get ready! - Three!

143
00:05:59,938 --> 00:06:01,968
