144
00:06:09,308 --> 00:06:10,607
(Laughing)

145
00:06:10,608 --> 00:06:11,617
She went down right away.

146
00:06:11,618 --> 00:06:13,717
(Screaming)

147
00:06:13,718 --> 00:06:17,618
(She beat Tarzan with her scream.)

148
00:06:18,558 --> 00:06:21,188
