152
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:27,828
Are you okay, Jun Myun?

153
00:06:28,998 --> 00:06:31,298
(I'm not okay.)

154
00:06:31,368 --> 00:06:32,497
The paddle board!

155
00:06:32,498 --> 00:06:33,638
