156
00:06:33,838 --> 00:06:35,367
Be careful! Here I come!

157
00:06:35,368 --> 00:06:36,568
(Dex is ready to make his jump.)

158
00:06:37,008 --> 00:06:39,478
(Dex makes his challenge with the Tarzan Swing.)

159
00:06:39,908 --> 00:06:41,978
(Dex will make his jump right away?)

160
00:06:42,908 --> 00:06:45,718
(Yes. That's right.)

161
00:06:58,928 --> 00:07:00,958
