165
00:07:16,578 --> 00:07:17,647
This is the best one.

166
00:07:17,648 --> 00:07:19,718
(Don't worry.)

167
00:07:20,118 --> 00:07:22,388
(I want to enjoy it as well.)

168
00:07:22,718 --> 00:07:24,988
Stay there. I'll go up.

169
00:07:26,288 --> 00:07:28,988
(Dex steps up.)

170
00:07:29,528 --> 00:07:31,958
