171
00:07:32,128 --> 00:07:33,728
Jun Myun looks so exhausted.

172
00:07:33,758 --> 00:07:35,568
Are you okay, Jun Myun?

173
00:07:35,728 --> 00:07:37,528
It looks like she's done for the day.

174
00:07:38,028 --> 00:07:39,267
It must've been tough for you...

175
00:07:39,268 --> 00:07:40,468
to do the same things as the young ones.

176
00:07:41,638 --> 00:07:44,208
(She used up all her strength after two dives.)

177
00:07:44,568 --> 00:07:46,808
(Exhausted Jun Myun joins the crowd.)

178
00:07:47,178 --> 00:07:48,207
That will work.

179
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:49,847
(Hye Yoon and Dex are getting ready again.)

180
00:07:49,848 --> 00:07:50,877
I'll pull it for you.

181
00:07:50,878 --> 00:07:52,277
- The direction. - This one will be straight.

182
00:07:52,278 --> 00:07:54,218
- Straight? Move forward? - One. Right.

183
00:07:54,948 --> 00:07:56,187
(Hye Yoon makes her challenge with the straight course.)

184
00:07:56,188 --> 00:07:57,787
Are you ready? Hold on.

185
00:07:57,788 --> 00:07:59,018
Hold on! Don't let go, Dex!

186
