188
00:08:06,328 --> 00:08:09,028
(I will pull it off this time.)

189
00:08:09,268 --> 00:08:12,268
One, two, three!

190
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,350
Hold on! Give me a moment!

191
00:08:15,308 --> 00:08:16,468
Gosh, our Hye Yoon!

192
00:08:17,668 --> 00:08:19,037
I'm scared again!

193
00:08:19,038 --> 00:08:21,038
Why did I set myself up for this again?

194
00:08:21,278 --> 00:08:22,308
Are you scared?

195
00:08:22,778 --> 00:08:24,608
It's okay!

196
00:08:25,178 --> 00:08:26,448
- One! - One!

197
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,310
Two!

198
00:08:29,688 --> 00:08:30,625
- Three! - Three!

199
00:08:33,358 --> 00:08:34,345
Jump!

200
00:08:38,128 --> 00:08:39,128
Jump!

201
00:08:40,158 --> 00:08:41,328
She did well.

202
00:08:46,298 --> 00:08:48,737
(Feeling happy)

203
00:08:48,738 --> 00:08:51,738
(Hye Yoon's second attempt is a great success.)

204
00:08:52,578 --> 00:08:54,508
(Gosh!)

205
00:08:54,938 --> 00:08:55,948
She's so cute.

206
00:08:57,478 --> 00:08:58,678
That was so exciting!

207
00:08:59,378 --> 00:09:00,518
Are you done now?

208
00:09:00,548 --> 00:09:01,648
Awesome.

209
00:09:02,818 --> 00:09:04,987
(I envy your youth.)

210
00:09:04,988 --> 00:09:06,417
- I'm going to get sick... - Let's go.

211
00:09:06,418 --> 00:09:07,858
while trying to have fun at this old age.

212
00:09:16,928 --> 00:09:18,798
(Oh, no!)

213
00:09:21,598 --> 00:09:23,807
(She really might get sick from this.)

214
00:09:23,808 --> 00:09:24,838
Gosh!

215
00:09:25,878 --> 00:09:27,838
It must've been really hot for her.

216
00:09:28,508 --> 00:09:30,648
(She accidentally makes a Dive into the Jungle.)

217
00:09:31,478 --> 00:09:33,378
(Struggling)

218
00:09:34,418 --> 00:09:35,618
I'll save you, Jun Myun!

219
00:09:36,288 --> 00:09:37,318
Gosh.

220
00:09:37,448 --> 00:09:38,558
Jun Myun!

221
00:09:39,458 --> 00:09:40,458
Jun Myun!

222
00:09:40,459 --> 00:09:41,858
(Hurry up!)

223
00:09:42,128 --> 00:09:44,358
(I'm coming as well.)

224
00:09:44,758 --> 00:09:47,398
I don't think I can make it back up on this again.

225
00:09:48,398 --> 00:09:51,068
(Going back and forth with the paddle board)

226
00:09:51,838 --> 00:09:54,438
(She barely manages to hold onto the board.)

227
00:09:55,038 --> 00:09:57,937
(A paddle of help)

228
00:09:57,938 --> 00:09:59,377
- Here. - I need to get up.

229
00:09:59,378 --> 00:10:00,508
I have to save her.

230
00:10:00,838 --> 00:10:02,408
Is it better to get on the boat?

231
00:10:02,678 --> 00:10:03,678
Gosh.
(Using all her might)

232
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,718
- Jun Myun. - No!

233
00:10:06,218 --> 00:10:07,817
- No! - It's flipping over!

234
00:10:07,818 --> 00:10:08,988
(Is she going to dive in again?)

235
00:10:09,088 --> 00:10:10,387
