241
00:10:18,028 --> 00:10:19,758
You should push her, Jung Ah.

242
00:10:20,798 --> 00:10:22,167
(I'll get to you, Jun Myun.)

243
00:10:22,168 --> 00:10:23,267
Help her.

244
00:10:23,268 --> 00:10:24,697
