248
00:10:28,968 --> 00:10:29,968
Like this!

249
00:10:29,969 --> 00:10:31,568
(I'll really come this time.)

250
00:10:32,008 --> 00:10:33,977
(She's struggling on her own.)

251
00:10:33,978 --> 00:10:35,208
(Laughing)

252
00:10:36,108 --> 00:10:38,348
(Take my hand, Jun Myun.)

253
00:10:39,018 --> 00:10:41,718
